{
  "info": {
    "name": "ShopFlow API",
    "description": "Coleção para exercitar a API do ShopFlow ponta a ponta pela borda (api-gateway :8080) com JWT do Keycloak.\n\nFluxo: rode `Auth > Obter token (customer)` (salva {{access_token}}); as demais requests já autenticam. Para `Stock` (role ADMIN), rode `Auth > Obter token (manager)` (salva {{admin_token}}).\n\nA SAGA é assíncrona — após o POST /orders, aguarde ~1s e consulte o pedido. Detalhes em ../doc/API.md.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      { "key": "token", "value": "{{access_token}}", "type": "string" }
    ]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "description": "Tokens JWT via password grant no Keycloak (realm shopflow, client shopflow-gateway).",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Obter token (customer)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.environment.set(\"access_token\", json.access_token);",
                  "pm.test(\"200 + access_token presente\", function () {",
                  "  pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "  pm.expect(json.access_token).to.be.a(\"string\");",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "urlencoded",
              "urlencoded": [
                { "key": "client_id", "value": "{{client_id}}", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "client_secret", "value": "{{client_secret}}", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "grant_type", "value": "password", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "username", "value": "{{customer_user}}", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "password", "value": "{{customer_password}}", "type": "text" }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{keycloak_url}}/realms/{{realm}}/protocol/openid-connect/token",
              "host": ["{{keycloak_url}}"],
              "path": ["realms", "{{realm}}", "protocol", "openid-connect", "token"]
            },
            "description": "Obtém um JWT do usuário CUSTOMER e salva em {{access_token}}. Rode esta request primeiro."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Obter token (manager)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.environment.set(\"admin_token\", json.access_token);",
                  "pm.test(\"200 + admin_token presente\", function () {",
                  "  pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "  pm.expect(json.access_token).to.be.a(\"string\");",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "urlencoded",
              "urlencoded": [
                { "key": "client_id", "value": "{{client_id}}", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "client_secret", "value": "{{client_secret}}", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "grant_type", "value": "password", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "username", "value": "{{manager_user}}", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "password", "value": "{{manager_password}}", "type": "text" }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{keycloak_url}}/realms/{{realm}}/protocol/openid-connect/token",
              "host": ["{{keycloak_url}}"],
              "path": ["realms", "{{realm}}", "protocol", "openid-connect", "token"]
            },
            "description": "Obtém um JWT do usuário ADMIN (manager) e salva em {{admin_token}}. Necessário para as requests de Stock."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Orders",
      "description": "Criação e consulta de pedidos. POST /orders exige role CUSTOMER; dispara a SAGA.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Criar pedido — caminho feliz (CONFIRMED)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.environment.set(\"order_id\", json.id);",
                  "pm.test(\"201 + PENDING\", function () {",
                  "  pm.response.to.have.status(201);",
                  "  pm.expect(json.status).to.eql(\"PENDING\");",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"customerId\": \"{{customer_id}}\",\n  \"items\": [\n    { \"productId\": \"{{product_id}}\", \"quantity\": 2, \"unitPrice\": 400.00 }\n  ]\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{gateway_url}}/orders",
              "host": ["{{gateway_url}}"],
              "path": ["orders"]
            },
            "description": "Total 2 x 400.00 = 800.00 (abaixo do limite do PSP). Nasce PENDING; após ~1s a saga conclui em CONFIRMED. Salva o id em {{order_id}}."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Criar pedido — cancela (CANCELLED)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.environment.set(\"cancel_order_id\", json.id);",
                  "pm.test(\"201 + PENDING\", function () {",
                  "  pm.response.to.have.status(201);",
                  "  pm.expect(json.status).to.eql(\"PENDING\");",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"customerId\": \"{{customer_id}}\",\n  \"items\": [\n    { \"productId\": \"{{product_id}}\", \"quantity\": 3, \"unitPrice\": 400.00 }\n  ]\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{gateway_url}}/orders",
              "host": ["{{gateway_url}}"],
              "path": ["orders"]
            },
            "description": "Total 3 x 400.00 = 1200.00 (>= limite do PSP) -> PaymentFailed -> ReleaseStock -> CANCELLED. Salva o id em {{cancel_order_id}}; consulte GET /orders/{{cancel_order_id}}."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Criar pedido — rejeita (REJECTED)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.environment.set(\"reject_order_id\", json.id);",
                  "pm.test(\"201 + PENDING\", function () {",
                  "  pm.response.to.have.status(201);",
                  "  pm.expect(json.status).to.eql(\"PENDING\");",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"customerId\": \"{{customer_id}}\",\n  \"items\": [\n    { \"productId\": \"a4444444-4444-4444-4444-444444444444\", \"quantity\": 1, \"unitPrice\": 400.00 }\n  ]\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{gateway_url}}/orders",
              "host": ["{{gateway_url}}"],
              "path": ["orders"]
            },
            "description": "Produto a4444444-... está sem estoque -> StockReservationFailed -> REJECTED (sem pagamento). Salva o id em {{reject_order_id}}; consulte GET /orders/{{reject_order_id}}."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Criar pedido — sem token (401)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"401 sem token\", function () {",
                  "  pm.response.to.have.status(401);",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"customerId\": \"{{customer_id}}\",\n  \"items\": [\n    { \"productId\": \"{{product_id}}\", \"quantity\": 2, \"unitPrice\": 400.00 }\n  ]\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{gateway_url}}/orders",
              "host": ["{{gateway_url}}"],
              "path": ["orders"]
            },
            "description": "Exemplo didático: sem Authorization, o gateway responde 401."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Consultar pedido",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"200\", function () {",
                  "  pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{gateway_url}}/orders/{{order_id}}",
              "host": ["{{gateway_url}}"],
              "path": ["orders", "{{order_id}}"]
            },
            "description": "Estado e itens do pedido. Após ~1s do caminho feliz, status = CONFIRMED."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Stock",
      "description": "Consulta de estoque. Exige role ADMIN — usa {{admin_token}} (rode Auth > Obter token (manager) antes).",
      "auth": {
        "type": "bearer",
        "bearer": [
          { "key": "token", "value": "{{admin_token}}", "type": "string" }
        ]
      },
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Listar estoque",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"200\", function () {",
                  "  pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{gateway_url}}/stock",
              "host": ["{{gateway_url}}"],
              "path": ["stock"]
            },
            "description": "Lista todos os itens de estoque (seed inicial). Com token de CUSTOMER retorna 403."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Consultar item",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"200\", function () {",
                  "  pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{gateway_url}}/stock/{{product_id}}",
              "host": ["{{gateway_url}}"],
              "path": ["stock", "{{product_id}}"]
            },
            "description": "Estoque de um produto (available/reserved). 404 (stock-item-not-found) se o productId não existir."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Payments",
      "description": "Consulta do pagamento de um pedido.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Pagamento por pedido",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"200\", function () {",
                  "  pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{gateway_url}}/payments/{{order_id}}",
              "host": ["{{gateway_url}}"],
              "path": ["payments", "{{order_id}}"]
            },
            "description": "Pagamento do pedido (status AUTHORIZED no caminho feliz). 404 (payment-not-found) se ainda não houver pagamento (ex.: pedido REJECTED)."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Notifications",
      "description": "Consulta das notificações registradas pelo notification-service.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Listar notificações",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"200\", function () {",
                  "  pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{gateway_url}}/notifications",
              "host": ["{{gateway_url}}"],
              "path": ["notifications"]
            },
            "description": "Lista as notificações (mais recentes primeiro)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Notificações por pedido",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"200\", function () {",
                  "  pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{gateway_url}}/notifications/{{order_id}}",
              "host": ["{{gateway_url}}"],
              "path": ["notifications", "{{order_id}}"]
            },
            "description": "Notificações do pedido. No caminho feliz: ORDER_CREATED + ORDER_CONFIRMED."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
